OL,3,CComedian with limb deformities hopes
OL,4,Clife story will inspire others
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports' Merseyside
OL,7,Fcorrespondent Andy Bonner speaks to
OL,8,FGary about the drama.
OL,10,FA Liverpool man born with deformities
OL,11,Fas a result of a medical scandal is
OL,12,Fhoping his life story can inspire
OL,13,Fothers who are struggling.
OL,15,FGary Skyner, now 66, was never
OL,16,Fexpected to live beyond 30 after his
OL,17,Fmother took a morning sickness pill
OL,18,Fwhich unwittingly caused severe birth
OL,19,Fdefects.
