OL,3,CComedian with limb deformities hopes
OL,4,Clife story will inspire others
OL,6,FThe story of their fight for justice
OL,7,Fhas been made into a hard-hitting
OL,8,Fplay, Mother's Ruin.
OL,10,FGary said, "We're living in an age
OL,11,Fwhere people are finding it hard to
OL,12,Fmake ends meet and people are giving
OL,13,Fup. Suicide rates are going up all the
OL,14,Ftime sadly.
OL,16,F"There's always another way. For me,
OL,17,Fyou show me a route and the blockages
OL,18,Fand I'll find a way through it."
