OL,6,FGary was one of Britain's first babies
OL,7,Fto be born of the thalidomide medical
OL,8,Fscandal in the late 1950s and early
OL,9,F1960s.
OL,11,FUnknown to his mum Frances, and more
OL,12,Fthan ten thousand other women around
OL,13,Fthe world, the morning sickness pill
OL,14,Fcaused birth defects.
OL,16,FHe was born in Toxteth in November
OL,17,F1959 with upper limb deformities and
OL,18,Fhearing problems.
