OL,6,FGary is probably best known for being
OL,7,Fa comedian, having appeared on ITV
OL,8,Fwith Jonathan Ross and counting Ricky
OL,9,FTomlinson amongst his friends.
OL,11,FBut he has had numerous jobs,
OL,12,Fincluding being employed as a welder
OL,13,Fand qualified football coach.
OL,15,FHe counts flying a plane and driving a
OL,16,Fcar to an advanced standard amongst
OL,17,Fhis accomplishments.
OL,19,F"The way I wouldn't want to be
OL,20,Fintroduced is, the poor disabled boy,"
OL,21,Fhe said.
